{"id": "1265692032962134100", "channel_id": "1265692032962134100", "type": 0, "author_id": "1073914607741177866", "author_name": "scholar_2", "author_bot": false, "content": "準備等第八章做一個容災環境專屬的評級，可能會找時間把隊伍都體驗一下，主要是投票看下大家想看角色版還是隊伍版", "timestamp": "2024-07-24T15:28:16.079000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1265692032962134100", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "容災推薦/梯度榜投票", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1265785568990859398", "channel_id": "1265785568990859398", "type": 0, "author_id": "1190088323709030423", "author_name": "steven09362", "author_bot": false, "content": "大佬们都说这期的融灾比较简单，再加上我可能运气比较好拿到了第一个融灾350分，刚刚创号一个月所以角色很不全，相信应该有很多跟我角色池类似的缺关键角色的玩家，所以放出来阵容跟大家分享，同时也欢迎大佬对我的阵容有什么地方需要改进进行交流讨论！（特别感谢泥工佬的二四）\n\n第一波 难度四  血肉毒队 （莉莉 小蜘蛛 伽伦 宁菲亚）\n        只拉了莉莉和宁菲亚，最开始打的是难度三感觉难度不大去凹了难度四，运气比较好一轮就过了，宁菲亚越高启越好！\n\n第二波 难度三  深海队 （小水母 米粒 墨菲 希莱斯特）\n         我的主c队，平时的主线都靠这套（希莱斯特换拉蒙那推主线），所以除了希莱斯特全升了，小水母伤害相比于图鲁还是有限，难度四打不过，但难度三我目前的练度绰绰有余。\n\n第三波 难度四  泥工佬队 （小骑士 朵儿 诺蒂拉 泥工佬的满配24）\n         感觉有了泥工佬在，游戏的性质就变了，从头脑风暴变成了轮椅玩家，其他角色不需要太高练度，二四单刷！感谢我的泥工佬！\n\n第四波 难度二  血肉队 （红夫人 蕾亚 艾继斯 潘迪亚）\n         没练度的血肉随便打了难度二，带潘迪亚是为了破反击，之前带的是莫名其妙抽出来了9只的艾尓瓦😭哪来的这么多艾娃，其他混沌角色一个抽不来。\n\n第五波 难度二  超维队 （萝坦 奥比岛 温科尔 环拉）\n         主c萝坦，我刚刚接触超维，感觉这个队伍需要一定的思考才能玩（可以参考女王之剑大佬的帖子），但爽也是挺爽的，奥尔拉的二启很重要，感谢女王之剑大佬的攻略和群里褂彩小童大佬的指点！\n\n这次应该是我第一次融灾凹到350比较激动，想跟大家分享一下，但我的游戏理解肯定没有老玩家那么深，我没有的羊妈、神父、二四、图鲁、栗子、大福、旺达吧啦吧啦这些角色替换到我目前的配队中肯定也会有更好的效果，希望各位校友都可以早日达成融灾350!\n\nuid：100568445 （各位校友加我一起玩！大佬也加加我，我借大佬们的满配唤醒体玩🥹）", "timestamp": "2024-07-24T21:39:56.806000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}, {"emoji": "🫠", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1265785569271611494", "filename": "Screenshot_20240724_220831.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 135280, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1265785568990859398/1265785569271611494/Screenshot_20240724_220831.jpg?ex=69fb0c6c&is=69f9baec&hm=b0dcbe315857ce8fb93d0efad9f4aa4422d60467c052bbbfec325d70d72edf31&"}, {"id": "1265785569628389386", "filename": "Screenshot_20240724_220819.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 127862, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1265785568990859398/1265785569628389386/Screenshot_20240724_220819.jpg?ex=69fb0c6c&is=69f9baec&hm=9cd68c44dd49424da7a67d9d04ac0c02115488181b3d1d52efafafbe41289fbc&"}, {"id": "1265785569934446612", "filename": "Screenshot_20240724_215327.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 174248, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1265785568990859398/1265785569934446612/Screenshot_20240724_215327.jpg?ex=69fb0c6d&is=69f9baed&hm=4996d62e868b0478d784b4100679a315ea3cef738c6ceb9ee5e6fa1ae444b634&"}, {"id": "1265785570265923685", "filename": "Screenshot_20240724_215333.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 178283, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1265785568990859398/1265785570265923685/Screenshot_20240724_215333.jpg?ex=69fb0c6d&is=69f9baed&hm=a68611275ee5113426e526ebe3657f2e20267bc93ce741c245e438816a4b58c8&"}, {"id": "1265785570555334777", "filename": "Screenshot_20240724_215339.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 172037, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1265785568990859398/1265785570555334777/Screenshot_20240724_215339.jpg?ex=69fb0c6d&is=69f9baed&hm=57a863a4abef84f35b2dba950db037f4ce8a876f6ab91c74466de4e35bbcff3c&"}, {"id": "1265785570878029884", "filename": "Screenshot_20240724_030503.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 174647, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1265785568990859398/1265785570878029884/Screenshot_20240724_030503.jpg?ex=69fb0c6d&is=69f9baed&hm=a96301184a161e75c8cebf226ebf2d7c8177433041132ad70119bac8e800f124&"}, {"id": "1265785571209642137", "filename": "Screenshot_20240724_215352.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 173080, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1265785568990859398/1265785571209642137/Screenshot_20240724_215352.jpg?ex=69fb0c6d&is=69f9baed&hm=b3cc8c2594251c38b8dc1eefd10ebe50901ac599d868a1aee291ba326894151f&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1265785568990859398", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "本期融灾350超低配阵容（刚入坑一个月无羊妈 神父 图鲁 二四等等等）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1174179680056791130"]}
{"id": "1265691340906303570", "channel_id": "1265691340906303570", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "大家好，这里是难忘今宵攻略组，本期为大家带来的是第13期「融灾禁区」地图。\n◆每两周刷新奖励与关卡，每个关卡只需要完成普通模式、困难或癫狂模式其中之一。\n\n◆经过毒地板（紫色格子）时，会扣除 血量上限 的约5%，也就是固定值。\n\n当踏入毒地板所扣除的血量被判断为致命伤害，则触发死亡抵抗/复活确认。\n\n◆同一关卡的各级警报地图都相同。\n\n▼▼▼\n\n【第1波】无光之境 - 间隙地图（混沌1，深海7，血肉5，超维3）\n\n【第2波】无光之境 - 间隙地图（混沌6，深海4，血肉2，超维8）\n\n【第3波】如图\n\n【第4波】幻梦深潜 - 戈利亚「复仇巨刃」地图（旧版）\n\n【第5波】意识潜游 - 艾瑞卡「扭曲核心」-声音如是说 地图\n\nuid100001547", "timestamp": "2024-07-24T15:25:31.080000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1265691341212352532", "filename": "Image_1721834330696.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 240948, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1265691340906303570/1265691341212352532/Image_1721834330696.jpg?ex=69fb5d6b&is=69fa0beb&hm=ac6155d1f9cc53c4c62cfa01fa891dd62658a31a0d44e0e073551f75ff79fa5e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1265691340906303570", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关卡地图「融灾禁区」总览ⅩⅢ", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1260133992636743681", "1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1265504980312526898", "channel_id": "1265504980312526898", "type": 0, "author_id": "1231540652253253705", "author_name": "menoctus", "author_bot": false, "content": "大家好，這裡是難忘今宵攻略組，這次為大家帶來的是奧爾拉支線地圖。\n\n（地圖皮膚忘了改）\n\n注意：\n\n紅地板「血污之池」：經過後消失，可選失去全部狂氣並刪除1張症狀卡/ 回復血量並被塞2張症狀卡；或在點亮共鳴【銀鑰洗禮】後，使用所有銀鑰能量清除。\n\nuid: 100001547\n\n新版：", "timestamp": "2024-07-24T03:04:59.252000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1265504982803939411", "filename": "LONG.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 3992195, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1265504980312526898/1265504982803939411/LONG.jpg?ex=69fb589b&is=69fa071b&hm=bd5d4d2ec0befa2aee949fb41fb7d8edbaf8e537da42858994b51bc2af765caf&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1265504980312526898", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "特遣紀錄「玫瑰的棲居」關卡地圖總覽", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1260133992636743681", "1181143392739147778"]}
